title: Rangers hold on for 3-2 victory over Blackhawks
text:
> Top News Rangers hold on for 3-2 victory over Blackhawks Chicago Blackhawks goalie Corey Crawford, center, saves against New York Rangers right wing Jesper Fast, left, and center Dominic Moore during the first period of an NHL hockey game Wednesday, Oct. 7, 2015, in Chicago.
